b'[![](../../cdshop/cdinfo.jpg)](../../cdshop/index.htm)  \n[Sacred Texts](../../index.htm)  [Hinduism](../index.htm)  [Index](index.htm)\n[Previous](av111.htm)  [Next](av113.htm)\n\n* * *\n\n## VI, 17. Charm to prevent miscarriage.\n\n1\\. As this great earth conceives the germs of the beings, thus shalt thy\nembryo be-beld fast, to produce a child after pregnancy!  \n2\\. As this great earth holds these trees, thus shall thy embryo be held fast,\nto produce a child after pregnancy!  \n3\\. As this great earth holds the mountains and the peaks, thus shall thy\nembryo be held fast, to produce a child after pregnancy!  \n4\\. As this great earth holds the animals scattered far, thus shall thy embryo\nbe held fast, to produce a child after pregnancy!\n\n* * *\n\n[Next: I, 11. Charm for easy parturition](av113.htm)\n\n'